      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an uncompromising example of the E92 M3, featuring the legendary S65 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8. This high-revving masterpiece delivers a linear power band up to its 8,400 RPM redline via eight individual throttle bodies. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission provides lightning-fast shifts, while the factory-spec Variable M Differential Lock ensures optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. The chassis remains rigid and unmolested, with the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) system providing precise damping adjustments for varied lateral load profiles. Meticulously maintained with documented preventative rod bearing and throttle actuator service, this vehicle represents a turn-key investment for the discerning collector seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
